These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, emerald
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, cycling
2 different games are played: scrabble, snooker
City: miami, marseilles
1. the person traveling to miami is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
2. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
3. the person who likes lavender is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Color      | emerald     | lavender      |
| Sport          | cycling | snowboarding    |
| Game         | snooker   | scrabble |
| City   | miami  | marseilles      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, october
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, italian
2 different pets are kept: bird, fish
City: hamburg, boston
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
2. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
3. the owner of the fish is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
4. the person traveling to hamburg is not the italian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Birthday    | january        | october    |
| Nationality       | turkish         | italian |
| Pet         | fish | bird   |
| City   | hamburg               | boston  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, white
City: nizza, liverpool
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, rock-climbing
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, aristoff
1. the person who's hobby is photography is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the right of the aristoff-smoker##8
3. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Color   | brown       | white |
| City   | nizza       | liverpool    |
| Hobby   | photography | rock-climbing |
| Cigar           | cain        | aristoff   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, marigold
There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, fuchsia
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, zombie
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, metal
1. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes fuchsia##5
2. the person who growsdahlia is not to the left of the fan of metal##8
3. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Flower         | marigold | dahlia  |
| Color           | fuchsia  | light-blue |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | animation   |
| Music-Genre     | metal   | punk |

