2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, prince
2 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, ambient
1. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the old-henry-smoker##8
3. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage   | juice | mirinda |
| Cigar   | prince    | old-henry     |
| Pet         | horse  | rabbit    |
| Music-Genre     | ambient     | hip-hop       |

