There are 2 different favourite colors: black, blue
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, montecristo
1. the person watching western movies is not to the left of the person who likes blue##8
2. the pall-mall-smoker is the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
4. the pall-mall-smoker is not to the right of the montecristo-smoker##8
5. the montecristo-smoker is not to the left of the person watching drama movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| Movie-Genre        | western | drama            |
| Color       | blue | black              |
| Beverage         | 7up  | lemonade |
| Cigar   | pall-mall     | montecristo         |

