.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-11::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, electrician
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, water
There 2 different types of food: peas, plum
City: berlin, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating peas##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is not the chef##6
4. the chef is not to the right of the person traveling to berlin##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Job   | chef      | electrician |
| Beverage   | cola    | water   |
| Food         | plum | peas     |
| City     | edinburgh | berlin  |

