The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, folk
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, sunflower
City: liverpool, rome
1. the person who growsdahlia is not to the right of the person watching sports movies##8
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |
| Movie-Genre          | sports         | musical    |
| Music-Genre           | punk | folk   |
| Flower   | dahlia   | sunflower    |
| City     | liverpool         | rome |

 